io.netty.channel

Class VoidChannel

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.netty.util.DefaultAttributeMap
      • io.netty.channel.AbstractChannel
        • io.netty.channel.VoidChannel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Channel, AttributeMap, Comparable<Channel>

    public final class VoidChannel
extends AbstractChannel
    A Channel that represents a non-existing Channel which could not be instantiated successfully.
